Product description

Are You Still Worried About Not Being Able To Pick Up Your phone To Answer Calls While Driving? Now You got a Good Solution for This Bad Situation!

SUNITEC Brand New Upgraded BC990P Bluetooth Car Speaker Can Give You A Solution That You Can Enjoy Your Crystal Clear Calling And Music No Matter Where You Are Without The Risk Of Getting Pulled Over.

Why Choose Us?

SUNITEC is a high-tech company with creativity and enterprising spirit. Since the company was established ten years ago, we have been deeply specilized in the field of car Bluetooth.

With leading experience and technology in Bluetooth transmission, audio analysis, speaker manufacturing, we are committed to providing a perfect wireless blue tooth hands free solution for phone in car. We have our own independent factory to produce independently designed products, creating high-quality products and trustworthy quality commitments to every customer.

Recommended:

  • Compatible with all Bluetooth enable smart device of Samgsung phone, iPhone, Pixels and other andriod cellular phones.
  • APO (Auto Power ON/OFF) Built-in vibration sensor for Auto On and Auto Off, when device is not in use to save battery life.
  • Multipoint Connecting Technology This upgraded handsfree car bluetooth speaker supports Apple Siri connection, can connect 2 cellphones simultaneously.

Please Note: If your garage is very nearby the house, the phone might still connect to your speakerphone when you are at home. So please manually turn it off before leaving the car or turn off Bluetooth from the phone to disconnect them FOR save battery energy.

Doesn't work / not recommended:

  • Not compatible with GPS navigators
  • Not compatible with smart watches
  • Can't take voice commands directly (must activate Siri Voice Assistant)

Hands free Calling Kit for Easy and Safe Driving Experience

What's in box

  • 1x BC990P hands free car bluetooth speaker for cell phone
  • 1x Magnetic sun visor clip
  • 1x Car charger
  • 1x Type-C USB cable
  • 1x Quick guide

  • Bluetooth version: V5.1
  • Operation Frequency Band: 2.4GHz~2.48GHz unlicensed ISM band
  • Built-in Battery: 1500mAh rechargeable battery

6W Powerful speaker loud enough for Old Cars Stereo Especially for truck

  • SUNITEC hands free phone device for car is specially designed for those who keen on convenient, free and wireless communication.
  • Press the phone icon MF-Button to activate Siri Voice Assistant for give your voice command to make outgoing calls, send texts.
  • Once Bluetooth paired, it will be automatically connected the knows phone next time when bluetooth speaker car kit is ON.
  • Operational temperature is +5 to + 40℃; Storage temperature is 0 to 70℃; Humidity 5-75% (no condensation)

  • It can use as a desk speakerphone for conference meeting
  • You can put it on your bag for music streaming everywhere you want.
  • A great gift for your father, husband and friends that no bluetooth on their car / truck.


6W Loud Speaker for quality audio

  • Built-in 6W (Dual 3W) multi-Midia powerful speakers to support crystal clear sound and loud volume even in noisy road, big enough for music streaming or calls.
  • With echo & background DSP noise-cancellation technology


Voice Instruction for GPS mps

  • Short press the phone icon button to activate Siri on your phone to give you voice commnd to get a driving directions for safe driving


Auto Power On & Reconnect

  • Built-in vibration sensor detects automatically turns on the car phone speaker kit, allowing the handsfree bluetooth to reconnect with your phone when your car door opens.
  • When device is not in use, the device will turn off automatically.

Intelligent Voice Guidance

You will hear voice guidance in the following situations from handsfree speaker phone: Power on; Power off; Pairing; Connected; Disconnected; Battery low, which make it easy to use.

Long Lasting Batty Life

With 1500mAh lithium-ion rechargable battery to support Up to 15 hours of REAL talking time, 1500 hrs of standby time.

3 hours to fully charged the hands free bluetooth phone speaker.

Support Multi-point connection

Sunitec BC990P bluetooth hands free phone speaker support multi connection can pairs two phones simultaneously and easily switch between music & calls.

  • Noted: CAN'T work with 2phones simultaneously only connected 2 phones , you can switch it on device to answer when got incoming calls.

Universal USB-C charging port

BC990P wireless speaker for cars made w/universal Type C charging port, so you don't need to worry lack of power, you can charge it with any other device's Type C cable.
